data.description: This awesome conveniently located Ottoville find doesn't come around often. With 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms and a full basement (mostly finished) it is just waiting for you to make it your own. This home has such great flow and many updates throughout including new paint, flooring, many light fixtures and a big back yard remodel as well for your awesome outdoor entertaining needs. The shed and new kitchen appliances that are just a few months old are included too.  Don't wait for this one because it won't last long. MOTIVATED SELLERS!!!
